description.description: The description of the Origin Access Control. Defaults to "Managed by Pulumi" if omitted.

etag.description: The current version of this Origin Access Control.

name.description: A name that identifies the Origin Access Control.

originAccessControlOriginType.description: The type of origin that this Origin Access Control is for. Valid values are `s3`, and `mediastore`.

signingBehavior.description: Specifies which requests CloudFront signs. Specify `always` for the most common use case. Allowed values: `always`, `never`, and `no-override`.

signingProtocol.description: Determines how CloudFront signs (authenticates) requests. The only valid value is `sigv4`.
